{"lastModified":1772145230291,"uri":"c::51632648983::vessel::14962070-1251-11f1-8af1-438fc022237c","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area:  Key West, Florida, USA, Fort Lauderdale, Miami\n\nThe Sea Ray 420 Sundancer is a timeless 46-foot luxury power yacht perfect for high-end day charters and relaxing overnight stays. Known for its comfortable layout and smooth performance, this express cruiser offers two cabins with two heads and two showers, comfortably sleeping up to six guests while accommodating up to 13 guests for day charters.\n\nEvery cabin has individual climate control systems for personalized comfort. With a cruising speed of around 18 knots and a top speed near 26 knots, the Sundancer blends performance with style. Based in Key West, Florida, this well-maintained yacht delivers a refined experience on the water.\n\nHighlights\n✓ Luxury power yacht in mint condition\n✓ Accommodates up to 13 guests by day and 6 overnight\n✓ 2 cabins, 2 heads, and 2 showers\n✓ Individual climate control in each cabin\n✓ Cruising speed of 18 knots, max speed 26 knots\n✓ Based in Key West, Florida","blueprint":{"name":"GRAND ADMIRAL","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::14962070-1251-11f1-8af1-438fc022237c::assets::0efccfa0-1257-11f1-b37e-fdb4755bfc69/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::14962070-1251-11f1-8af1-438fc022237c::assets::0eeeecf0-1257-11f1-b37e-fdb4755bfc69/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::14962070-1251-11f1-8af1-438fc022237c::assets::0efe0820-1257-11f1-b37e-fdb4755bfc69/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::14962070-1251-11f1-8af1-438fc022237c::assets::0eee9ed0-1257-11f1-b37e-fdb4755bfc69/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::14962070-1251-11f1-8af1-438fc022237c::assets::0ef09aa0-1257-11f1-b37e-fdb4755bfc69/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::14962070-1251-11f1-8af1-438fc022237c::assets::0efc3360-1257-11f1-b37e-fdb4755bfc69/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::14962070-